INSERT INTO `event` (`id`, `name`, `image`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 'Ensuring studying and working in the hot season', 'https://www.baodanang.vn/dataimages/202006/original/images1564178_nang_nong.jpg', 'In hot weather of nearly 40oC, workers in construction sites, sanitation workers ... still work hard to keep pace, clean streets and fight against pollution; students still go to school to study. To ensure the health of the la', '2020-07-01 04:47:58', '2020-07-21 04:48:16'),
(2, 'Experience exploring nature', 'https://www.baodanang.vn/dataimages/202006/original/images1563741_SONTRA.jpg', 'The \"green lung\", the \"jewel\" of Da Nang, the \"home\" of the primate queen ... are beauties from friends from all directions talking about Son Tra peninsula. Coming to this beautiful peninsula, visitors will not be surprised at the primeval forest containing the typical values ​​of biodiversity, history and culture.The vivid beauty of Son Tra makes many people flutter. Photo: NGUYEN KHOA DONG\r\nThe vivid beauty of Son Tra makes many people flutter. Photo: NGUYEN KHOA DONG\r\nAddress must come in the summer\r\n\r\nSon Tra has a lot of potential for eco-tourism exploitation. Only 10km from the city center, the topography of the subtropical rainforest like Son Tra is a rare form of terrain. Although Son Tra is not too large (about 60km2 in area, 13km in length and 5km in width), it converges the beauty of forests, mountains and the sea.\r\n\r\nLocated in a cool and fresh climate, with beautiful natural scenery along with rich flora and fauna, Son Tra brings together all elements for visitors to relax, organize fun activities, and plug in. Camp, picnic and discover the thrilling little adventure of pristine mountains. Ms. Duong Thi Xuan Lieu, Head of Tourism Management and Exploitation Department in Son Tra Peninsula (Son Tra Peninsula Management Board and Danang tourism beaches) said that during the period of strong tourism development in Vietnam. Currently, besides the comfortable and luxurious resort services, the type of tourism that many travelers are interested in is tourism experience, nature discovery. Son Tra meets most of the needs of this guest market.Tourists coming to Da Nang city all want to visit Son Tra famous landmarks such as Linh Ung Pagoda, Ban Tien Tien, Ban Banyan Tree, and explore natural forests. “For many years, the trekking walking route discovered some of the typical plant species in Son Tra and found interesting stories around these species of trees that many tourists have chosen. Many young people prefer to go to Vong Canh House, located at an altitude of 550m above the sea, this is an ideal viewing spot. On sunny days, visitors can enjoy panoramic views over Hai Van Pass, Ngoc Island and Danang Bay. After enjoying the beautiful natural scenery, visitors can witness the 29 radar station and discover interesting stories around these places, ”Ms. Lieu said.The best time to visit this place is from March to September. At this time, the weather is sunny, dry, rarely stormy. This is also the best time for Son Tra in the year with the changing seasons. If going in the winter, it is easy to encounter fog, difficult to ensure safety when moving. Currently, the travel companies have put into operation the terrestrial tours such as: exploring Son Tra, exploring the jungle in the heart of the young streets, visiting Da Nang - Son Tra by helicopter, the route \"Green Space\" ... and underwater tours such as fishing with fishermen, scuba diving to see the coral ...\r\n\r\nAn advantage when exploring Son Tra is the extremely convenient and easy path. Guests can visit, visit and experience by their own means or can rent a motorbike, taxi, car to travel if traveling with family, group of people. Recently, the Management Board of Son Tra Peninsula and Da Nang tourist beaches have issued a specific transfer service fee for each route in turn of VND 45,000 for route 1 (9km from the car park to serve APEC for sightseeing. banyan tree tree heritage); VND 60,000 for route 2 (35 km, from the entrepot parking area - Yet Kieu - Ban Ban peak - North beach - banyan tree - Linh Ung pagoda - entrepot parking); VND 80,000 for route 3 (32 km, from the transit car park - Yet Kieu - Om stream - Vong Canh house - transit car park).Along with that, the Management Board has installed 3 guard posts at the checkpoints; installing electric lighting system, signal lights, manual barie; Mobile toilets at transfer car parks, waiting rooms, benches, parasols, signs, illuminating tourist routes ... In the coming time, the Management Board proposed installing a ne', '2020-07-01 04:52:22', '2020-07-27 04:52:27'),
(3, 'Maintain a safe and attractive destination', 'https://www.baodanang.vn/dataimages/202006/original/images1564186_3__3_6__duy_tri.jpg', 'The city promotes and promotes safe, friendly and attractive Da Nang destinations; supporting tourism businesses to restore business activities; promptly deploy solutions to stimulate tourism, communication and market orientation in accordance with the new situation to attract tourists to Da Nang ...\r\n\r\nThose are the key contents of the Covid-19 tourism restoration plan, which was strongly implemented in the coming time by the city\'s tourism industry.\r\n\r\nDa Nang needs more new products to attract customers. In the photo: Domestic tourists after visiting Thanh Dien Hai and Da Nang Museum. Photo: THU HA\r\nDa Nang needs more new products to attract customers. In the photo: Domestic tourists after visiting Thanh Dien Hai and Da Nang Museum. Photo: THU HA\r\nEnsure safe destination to Da Nang\r\n\r\nAccording to a report of the Department of Tourism, in the first 6 months of 2020, the total number of tourists visiting and visiting Da Nang was estimated at more than 1.49 million, down 64.8% compared to the same period in 2019, of which national visitors international visitors is estimated at more than 598 thousand arrivals, down 66.1% over the same period of 2019, domestic tourists are estimated to reach over 893 passengers, down 64% over the same period of 2019. Total tourism revenue is estimated at 5,952 billion Dong, down 59 , 5% over the same period in 2019.Deputy Director of the City Tourism Department Nguyen Xuan Binh said that in the last 6 months of 2020, the city tourism industry will focus on the domestic tourist market. Accordingly, in the immediate period, to focus on attracting tourists from nearby localities, convenient to move in the Central - Highlands provinces (Quang Tri, Quang Binh, Thua Thien Hue, Quang Nam, Binh Dinh ...) .); coordinate with airlines and tour operators to exploit passengers from localities with direct flights to Da Nang (Hanoi, Ho Chi Minh City, Can Tho, Hai Phong, Quang Ninh, Pleiku, Phu Quoc ) ...\r\n\r\nAt the same time, diversify and improve the quality of short-term tourism products, marine leisure tourism products, leisure tourism, ecology, marine sports, leisure tourism, health care, points. new check-in; developing official tourism products (MICE), entertainment, team building ...Along with welcoming and organizing to serve tourists in the domestic market, the tourism industry also has many solutions to ensure the safety of Da Nang destination, with the development and implementation of a set of safety criteria in restoration. tourism services, travel services, hotels, tourist attractions and transportation, which will carry out synchronous sanitation, protection, sterilization, disinfection and water equipment. handwashing, epidemic prevention measures at all tourist service establishments in the area; launch the Da Nang movement \"safe destination\" to ensure the safety for tourists and staff of tourism service business units, hotels, tourist transportation units, tourist destinations and tourist beaches in the city to make visitors feel more secure and comfortable ...\r\n\r\nEnhancing communication and attracting customers\r\n\r\nResponding to the tourism stimulus program \"Vietnamese people travel Vietnam\" of the Vietnam National Administration of Tourism, the city\'s tourism industry organized the announcement of tourism stimulus in 2020 to promote and promote destinations. Danang is safe, friendly and attractive.With the program \"Da Nang gratitude - Danang Thank You 2020\" from May to December 2020, the products, services and services are attractive, quality assurance to bring more added value to Tourists with service groups include: sightseeing tours; stay; Eating; shopping; entertainment - tourist area; health care; transportation (air transport services; transportation services at the destination and cruise ship services) ...\r\n\r\nEnsure tourism environment to attract guests. In the photo: Tourists have fun at Da Nang beach. Photo: THU HA\r\nEnsure tourism environment to attract guests. In the photo: Touri', '2020-07-01 04:56:18', '2020-07-29 04:56:23');

