(1, 'My Khe beach in Danang', 'https://sites.google.com/site/dulichdanang365/_/rsrc/1560331354632/bai-bien-da-nang/bai-bien-my-khe-da-nang/Bai-Bien-My-Khe2.jpg', 'Hoang sa, Ngu Hanh Son, Da Nang', 'America\'s leading economic magazine Forbes has voted My Khe Beach in Danang as one of the six most attractive beaches on the planet. It can be said that My Khe Beach has met all the basic criteria of Forbes, such as: My Khe Beach is convenient for transportation, the beach is free for all visitors, Beach has shore. long and flat sand, sunshine and wave levels suitable for playing sports, capable of ensuring safety for tourists, luxury resorts, villas of international standards ...\r\n\r\n\r\nbeautiful sea view\r\nA corner of My Khe Beach Danang\r\nThe Sunday Herald Sun of Australia also commented that My Khe Beach is one of the 10 most popular Asian beaches in the world.\r\n\r\nDa Nang is home to many beautiful and famous beaches such as Nam O Beach, My Khe Beach, Tien Sa Beach, Non Nuoc Beach ... Of which, My Khe Beach has a length of about 900m Beach is one of the busiest and very familiar to all city residents as well as international visitors.My Khe Beach is famous for its fine white sand, mild waves, warm water all year round, and beautiful and beautiful coconut trees surrounded. Tourists can swim in the sea almost year-round, but most suitable in the summer, from May to August. Not to mention, because the coast is not deep, guests will feel secure while swimming and relaxing to watch the majestic Marble Mountains and Cu Lao Cham island far from Hoi An ...\r\n\r\nBai Bai My Da Da slot\r\nWith a salinity of about 60% and no pollution, the water is rated highly safe. Therefore, there are many corals, rich source of flora and fauna along the coast. In particular, the types of valuable algae such as yellow seaweed, duckweed seaweed have high export value.\r\n\r\nLike other beaches of Danang, My Khe develops quite well the types of services for tourists such as fishing, windsurfing, diving, yacht. The beach has a rescue system including a watchtower, a life buoy, a flag for swirling water and a rescue force is on duty day and night, ready to respond promptly when people are in distress.Hoang hon on the slot\r\nWhen sunset came, My Khe put on a new coat with a quieter, quieter color. It feels like a sudden slack.\r\n\r\nIn the summer, My Khe coastal hotels in Da Nang are the first priority of travelers, you want to book My Khe coastal hotels with good prices, please contact: 0981166889, respectfully serve.\r\n\r\nBooking of hotels in beautiful coastal city of danang\r\nTourists are fond of hotels near My Khe beach in the summer\r\n\r\nMy Khe beach stretches\r\nMy Khe Beach in Da Nang is wide and fine white sand\r\n\r\nMy Khe beach said no to garbage\r\n\r\nPlease see My Khe beach location on Google Map', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQGELh6rVI2BAw_sNu2CGmGY-yphlpheZrsgg&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTfJ9EVpXBifTS-wdTj-r5sVR3TO1JDRgcG5w&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQpyPYdMILalaIFTtBbTYv9EJbELzRNkiADww&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRxLythlZUpvkyJhHDcRdJYjBKLVm6yVyAq1w&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSovwh0Z1fo8MDw1PHZGpAOq-GexIvI8VOmrA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTqSjxF-v6OAj5Xywzi1XxlaLOhlKx8LKHQEg&usqp=CAU', 1, '16.061756', '108.246938'),
(2, 'Visiting Huyen Khong Khong - Strangely Lost In Tien Canh', 'https://mytourcdn.com/upload_images/Image/Tuan%20NL/dong%20Huyen%20Khong/7220018876_0759c14c4e_z.jpg', 'Hoa Hai, Ngu Hanh Son, Da Nang Vietnam', 'Located in the famous Ngu Hanh Son complex, Huyen Khong is one of the most beautiful, most fanciful and has the greatest spiritual value. Huyen Khong Cave is an open cave, circular arch, flat background, on the arch has 5 openings to the outside, light coming in here creates a mysterious atmosphere shimmering for the cave.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n Huyen Khong Cave is one of the most beautiful, most fanciful and has the greatest spiritual value\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nSee more: Hotels in Danang\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nIt is one of the famous Marble Mountains caves\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nTo get into Huyen Khong cave, you have to step down more than 20 steps deeper than Hoa Nghiem cave about 5m, likened to a bell face down, which is one of the largest, coolest and most beautiful caves of Ngu Hanh Son population. The dynamic dome is exposed to the outer space, the light shines in to make it more dazzling. On a sunny day, the cave is like a natural air conditioner with cool and fresh air.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSunny sunshine and cool, fresh air\r\nThis is what makes the difference of Huyen Khong cave to some other caves in Ha Long, Phong Nha - Ke Bang ... While the majority of places are cavernous, moist, in the cave must be lighted or when entering the right If there is a light, Huyen Khong Cave is not a bit of stalactite, but it has enough ventilation and natural light.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHuyen Khong Cave is quite open and full of natural light\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nAt the top is the statue of Thich Ca Buddha, made in 1960 by artisan Nguyen Chat, who is famous in Non Nuoc stone carving village. Below is the altar of Bodhisattva Ksitigarbha Buddha. On the left of the cave, there is a temple of Ngoc Phi (Mrs Chua Tien), a place where visitors come to pray and pray for fortune; Lady Lầu Phi temple (Lord Ngàn Ngàn) is visited by prayers for health and peace.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTfUvW_eEr-Tr8HsbOq-cLjOq2o_EMB44oPRg&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSiICvtkM7h1MnRYs11Uet2q_WCeHsREhit4w&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcR3pAdZIpoqadZatXmKqXIOwOh2cVL3M6o45A&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT3hYUZlruCZ0gS_RQWMbLSbejT5vDcnrNwsA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTXkhU6hks_70lLu3H-ysP1ZIUGMoXzGhcp0Q&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT6Xr-eY2UdfhuhLLQO0MZ-Ho05SsUWUa1dcw&usqp=CAU', 1, '16.017558', '108.260554'),
(3, 'Discover the Am Phu Cave', 'https://danangsensetravel.com/view/at_kham-pha-dong-am-phu-da-nang_221bb899e8d81652a38e159720ac4313.jpg', 'Hoa Hai, Ngu Hanh Son, Da Nang, Vietnam', 'Take visitors to the coastal city where owns unique beauty, ideal for owning beautiful white sand beaches with the most attractive beach on the planet, mountains, passes, remote resorts most flowers in the world. In addition, Da Nang has a cave located under the mountains in Ngu Hanh Son scenic area, Am Phu cave is the longest and most mysterious cave in Da Nang.\r\nExploring Da Nang Am Phu Cave - Photo 1\r\nAm Phu Cave is located in Thuy Son, high arch, with places from 45m to 50m high. This is a natural cave, but the cave images are random in accordance with the law of cause and effect of the Buddha, simulating the realms where people will enjoy life or suffer retribution after death.At the entrance of the cave are sandstone walls, on the right is Mr. Thien, on the left is Mr. Evil. Thich Hue Hung, who presided over the restoration and restoration of the Underworld cave for three years (2003-2006), said that people who behave in the general life are in both good and evil karma. If good deeds will go to Thien Thai Gioi, the name of a canyon is on the left of the road to the cave. If you know how to cultivate the mind of nature, make good and avoid evil, you will go to the Earth Store Bodhisattva Bodhisattva at Jizō, the most solemn and spacious place. If sowing evil karma, depending on the severity and exile, they will be exiled to 10 hell realms, of which A Pi hell is the deepest place in the heart of Hades.\r\nExploring Da Nang Am Phu Cave - Photo 2Many intuitive images teach people near good and evil. Judge Quan Dien with the scale of Nature considers the merits / crimes of each person, behind the body of the scale is engraved with the words \"Thien hammock, infant illegally\" (The sky cage is sparse, sparse but difficult to fall). The Glass Director at Minh Vuong Palace was like an eye to the evil stories of each person and rewarded or punished. Sam Xinhai with the image of two hands supporting the fire heart has the word Tam. At the end of the cave is A Pi prison, where the image of Maudgalyāyana, a true religious monk, for loving his mother, Thanh De, was exiled for causing many bad karma and went to save his mother ...\r\nExploring Da Nang Am Phu Cave - Photo 3\r\nThe Underworld is a harmonious combination of folk philosophy and Buddhism. The mystical legends that pop from the natural and human images create the essence not to create a strong feeling for the viewer but mainly to transform the human character, convert evil, regulate and heal evil. create a good neighbor.\r\nExploring Da Nang Am Phu Cave - Photo 4In the theory of yin and yang, the life of people and things is always the opposite. Therefore, in the Underworld there is also a path to heaven like the division between Evil and Good. Different from the road to hell, the way to Heaven is the steps covered with natural light. Area \"peak sky\" facing the sea. Below is Non Nuoc fine arts village and the scenery is very poetic.\r\n \r\nVisiting Am Phu Cave of Ngu Hanh Mountain, visitors not only admire the marvelous natural tectonics, but also learn many interesting folktales, imbued with the profound doctrines at the door of Buddha.', 'https://danangsensetravel.com/view/at_kham-pha-dong-am-phu-da-nang_b18ec9997a5ca027a495f93592f7e95c.jpg@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSjNEY5k54hHFqx4puNtSqIraM_Bdp0v-PoDQ&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSd1Q1qrn_vJvQDeWH1d98T-JzlSFCRsHjkNw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRUufs__4zt1c8WHxeH1-j-66ZS2ntv3PMOrw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcR7jdp9HlYoBcU_V0ZvW_CpysR8mZZ-is3xlA&usqp=CAU', 1, '16.003269', '108.264149'),
(4, 'Van Thong Cave - Thuy Son Mountain', 'http://docs.portal.danang.gov.vn/images/images/chuyende/nguhanhson/dongVanThong.jpg', 'Hoa Hai, Ngu Hanh Son, Da Nang, Vietnam', 'Van Thong cave, also known as \"the way to the sky\", is located within the mountain, the dark cave\'s entrance, the deeper and narrower the deeper it reaches.\r\n\r\nIn the middle of the cave, there is a large stone Buddha image, 205cm high, 50cm horizontal body, standing posture, arms stretched straight along the body, left hand held high forward, posture to press seals.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIn addition, in the cave, there is a chewing stele engraved directly on the cave wall, inscribed with the Chinese words \"Five Aggregates of Fairy Buddha Kill Lac\", now the words on the stele have been worn out and difficult to read. The stele was erected in the year of the Goat (1631), during the Nguyen Dynasty, shaped quite stylishly and symbolically. It is a small temple with a roof and bends. The distance between the roof and the heart of the stele is cut into nine cells, each engraved with one word, inscribed with the name of the Five Aggregates painted with Buddha passed away. The sides and lower borders are decorated with flowers and vines. Beer is 74 cm high and 64 cm wide; the forehead is 14 cm high; 4cm wide bezels. The heart of the stele engraved 14 lines. The content of the epitaph said: Bhikkhu Hue Dao Minh, Du Xuyen commune, Le Duong district, Thang Hoa government, Quang Nam land, Dai Viet residence maintained enlightenment, restoration, burning incense to bless the saint, and dedicate three jewels to handed down for thousands of generations. Praying for the motherhood, sentient beings of the dharma world, a heart of destiny in the blissful world of Amitabha Buddha. Next are the Buddhist Dharma\'s vows and praises.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSqKtJg8wBbM3NM7Z8hNeebJCsuAKudp3t_Kw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT-ZomXLPDMvgUAzD4V34UBP2re4BE9d7UaYA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSYUiZUk4gcbzJLVPT43D1P3AA869VRjT09HA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQrbkTw0A3TFGQNbDAZYM35NPlLCetHuahscg&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQMFGE-v1RXhVLVcsLPOae_GT6hDrVDvjFZjA&usqp=CAU', 1, '16.003834', '108.263495'),
(5, 'Memory Coffee', 'https://dranahotel.com/upload/iblock/f.jpg', '07 Bach Dang, Hai Chau 1, Hai Chau, Da Nang', 'Memory Restaurant Cafe, the leaves on the Han River. Memory has become a unique mark of Danang tourism city. Memory wears a sparkling beauty and very modern appeal. When traveling to Da Nang, remember to visit Memory Lounge to feel the strange beauty of this cafe.\r\n\r\nAddress: 7 Bach Dang, Hai Chau, Da Nang\r\nPhone: (84-8) 511 357 5899.\r\n\r\nHan River is considered a symbol of Da Nang. Memory leaf has gradually become a symbol of the Han River when it is located in a very beautiful and favorable position on the Han River, along Bach Dang Street, the most wonderful street in Da Nang. Viewed from above, Memory Lounge is like a giant leaf floating in the middle of a stream. Memory really becomes a highlight for Da Nang tourism.\r\n\r\nmemory-lounge-da-nang\r\nBeautiful memory floats on the Han River next to the rotating bridge.The poetic Han River bends and hugs the gentle city of Danang to your heart. Han River Bridge is the first rotating bridge in Vietnam and also the pride of the city people. Han River seems to wear a colorful shirt at night whenever the bridge turns on a light. The colorful lights increase the beauty of the city at night. For a long time, Han River has been an interesting place to visit whenever anyone has the opportunity to visit this beautiful city of Danang. Where Danang residents and tourists often come to enjoy the windy feeling from the Han River and see the beauty of this bridge.\r\n\r\nmemory-lounge\r\nThe front of the Memory overlooks Bach Dang street\r\n\r\nGiant Leaf Memory Lounge, with unique architecture. Memory Lounge is modern, not an ancient cafe, but harmonized with the beautiful natural landscape. The shape of the leaf is not only in the overall exterior architecture but it also shows the unity in every corner of the interior, each pattern on the walls, ceiling and pillars when entering the interior area of ​​the restaurant. Memory makes anyone admire at the first sight. Memory\'s rooms are designed with outstanding glass so that anywhere in the Memory Lounge we can capture the best images of the Han River, the swing bridge and the streets of Danang.Quay-cafe-memory\r\nMemory cafe\r\n\r\nWith a capacity of 350 seats, Memory Lounge is invested with a 5-star standard including a restaurant, bar and 03 cozy VIP rooms. The ground floor and river bank are designed for coffee and breakfast. The first floor is a bar area and a system of VIP rooms with a unique space sitting in the middle of an interesting leaf floating on the Han River. In addition to other luxurious menus, Memory Lounge also meets the needs of high-class guests, merchants and visitors to Da Nang with high-end menus such as micro fish soup, bird\'s nest, abalone ... processing right level.\r\n\r\nWith service time:\r\n\r\nBar - Cafe - Snack | 7:00 \'- 23:30\'\r\nBreakfast | 7:00 \'- 10:30\'\r\nNoon | 11:00 \'- 14:30\'\r\nEvening | 17:00 \'- 22:30\'\r\n\r\nPrice: 50,000 - 250,000 VND\r\n\r\nThe price of a drink is from 50,000VND upwards, bringing a very special and luxurious flavor.\r\n\r\nMemory Lounge owns a rich wine list of nearly 100 brands imported from famous wine-making families in the world, including the most precious and rare bottles of wine in Vietnam and the world. bring into service. With an airy space, a diverse menu of Asian dishes and professional service, Memory Lounge deserves a place for intimate or formal gatherings, meaningful activities. class level.space-memory\r\nAn angle in the space of memory\r\n\r\nThe \"Memory Lounge\" is really a unique cultural and architectural highlight of Da Nang, a place to meet friends, work with partners, a relaxing space for anyone to find, It is a strange place to see and reflect on Da Nang. It is like hugging Danang to eyes.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSO1vGBwlJZNA26rouT1iGER_MVjM9zDEfe6A&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQPgpOR66alW9mm3cEibvuGOttvJyYtogDEqg&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRvMlWnbZimTaqkuk4pakUdCRHYlON7yTUeUA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQQWSFm44od8R8QO9PSRVTtqh9v9ld1uMb-4g&usqp=CAU', 17, '16.072933', '108.225220'),
(6, 'Pool House Restaurant', 'https://sites.google.com/site/hyattdanangresort/_/rsrc/1468929239690/nha-hang/pool-house/nha-hang-pool-house-hyatt-danang.jpg', 'Truong Sa, Hoa Hai, Ngu Hanh Son', 'Located on a romantic beach with white sand and tranquility, Hyatt Regency Danang Resort and Spa is an ideal place to explore the exotic beauty of the central city of Vietnam on any occasion, from meetings to events. events or family memorable vacation.\r\n\r\nHyatt Regency Danang Resort and Spa is the second hotel of the prestigious American Group in Vietnam. As one of the largest 5-star luxury resorts in Danang, Hyatt Regency Danang Resort and Spa is known as one of the most impressive destinations today.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Resort consists of 200 luxurious rooms with spacious balconies and large windows, 182 luxury apartments and 27 sea villas with private pools.\r\n\r\nThe unique feature of each villa is that the distance to the sea is different, so each gives you different experiences. From 3 apartment buildings from 6 to 12 floors, the apartments are arranged staggeredly connected to the entire glass-covered facade but still bring a warm and safe feeling, comfort for residents. Wooden furniture are all artistic products that bring a modern but bold atmosphere.\r\n\r\nRESTROOMHyatt Regency Danang Resort & Spa with modern design and Vietnamese style architecture, the interior is arranged in oriental art, creating a unique relaxation of Asia.\r\n\r\nOffering guests a wide choice of guest room types, all rooms offering beautiful sea views, Hyatt Regency Danang Resort & Spa includes 198 guest rooms and high-class apartments, 160 one-bedroom apartments. up to three bedrooms and 22 villas including 3 bedrooms.\r\n\r\nHyatt Guest Room (1 King Bedroom and 2 Twin Bedrooms)\r\n\r\nWith a modern design, the tones flooded with sunlight. The interior is made of local wood, arranged in oriental art, creating an unmistakable Asian space among modern amenities.\r\n\r\nWith transparent floor-to-ceiling windows, exterior lighting spills into the 42-square-meter room and the bed is covered with feather pillows. With amenities: separate shower, bathtub, spacious wardrobe and long sofa, the room will give you an extremely comfortable holiday.Ocean View Guest Room (King Bed Ocean View and Twin Beds Ocean View)\r\n\r\nhyatt-regency-danang-resort-and-spa\r\nhyatt-regency-danang-resort-and-spa\r\nImmerse yourself in the panorama of one of the best ocean views. The sea view will bring you a relaxing and comfortable feeling in a spacious space with a cool climate right at the romantic beach in Da Nang.\r\n\r\nClub Access (1 King Bed with Club Access and 2 Twin Beds With Club Access)\r\n\r\nhyatt-regency-danang-resort-and-spa\r\nhyatt-regency-danang-resort-and-spa\r\nThis 42 m² room has a spacious living area. Club Access guests will enjoy the Regency Club benefits: access to the private pool, daily breakfast and hourly cocktails. The luxurious interior combined with soft sofas and sofas will give visitors the best experience when coming to Hyatt Regency Danang Resort & Spa\r\n\r\n3 Bedroom Ocean VillaThe 307 m² villa has a master bedroom with a king size bed, a second bedroom with 2 single beds and a bedroom with an extra bed for the butler. This is the high class room of Hyatt Regency Danang Resort & Spa\r\n\r\nAmenities included in this room include: Discounts for spa services, gyms, etc. A separate swimming pool and a large yard to easily party, bring a sense of comfort and relaxation to visitors. here.\r\n\r\n3 Bedroom Ocean Front Villa\r\n\r\nThe 307 m² villa has a master bedroom with a king size bed, a second bedroom with 2 single beds and a bedroom with an extra bed for the butler. This is the high class room of Hyatt Regency Danang Resort & Spa\r\n\r\nhyatt-regency-danang-resort-and-spa 5\r\n\r\nBooking here, visitors just steps from the green shoreline of Danang. The facilities attached to this room category include: Discounts for spa services, gym,