(16, 'Highland Coffee Danang', 'https://monngondathanh.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/highland1-min.jpg', 'The first Highland Danang cafe was a branch in Indochina building in 2009. At the same time Da Nang transformed itself and developed and urbanized. Not until the end of 2016', 'The Difference makes Highland Highland Cafe Danang attracts many customers\r\nThe first Highland Danang cafe was a branch in Indochina building in 2009. At the same time Da Nang transformed itself and developed and urbanized. By the end of 2016, the Highland coffee chain continued to explode and opened many other branches in the young city.\r\n\r\nHighland\'s customer segments are mostly office workers, tourists and young people. With most opening in locations are commercial centers or large buildings.Currently, it can be affirmed that Highland Cafe Danang is the most successful chain here. The shop is always crowded. And if you go on the weekends, it is difficult to find a seat.\r\n\r\nTo such sustained success. Highland always focuses on serving customers with the best service. Invest in furniture and space very well. Bring satisfaction to customers. And product quality is always a top priority of highland.Cafe is one of the products that make up the Highland brand. From the stage of selecting the beans to preparation. All things have a strict process and different formula. Milk coffee is the most popular dish. Perhaps because of the combination of strong milk and coffee flavor, it creates a special coffee that is nowhere to be found.Choose prime locations. With a view overlooking the Han River, the bridges and the streets of Danang. Sitting at the bar can also free the view of a part of the city. So diners love to choose Highland as a meeting place, chatting weekend with friends, family ...', 'https://danangaz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/phin-cf-n%C3%A9n.jpg@https://danangaz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/kh%C3%B4ng-gian-n%C3%A9n.jpg@https://danangaz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/th%C3%AAm-n%C3%A9n.jpg@https://danangaz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/phin-s%E1%BB%AFa-n%C3%A9n.jpg@https://danangaz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/freeze-n%C3%A9n-747x420.jpg', 6, '16.065948', '108.224370'),
(17, 'Thien Duyen Vegetarian Restaurant', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQbFoN_DKwlxfdqDiCEfKaL8mddv9WHDLuCQA&usqp=CAU', 'Thien Duyen Vegetarian Restaurant - 308 Hoang Dieu, Binh Hien Ward, Hai Chau District', 'Thien Duyen vegetarian restaurant is loved by many Da Nang diners as well as tourists because of its delicious, very good taste, especially on the full moon days, the first day is always crowded with customers coming in and out. The menu of the restaurant includes a variety of dishes from rice, noodles, noodles, soup bread to breakfast cakes such as filter cake, pancakes, dumplings, wrapping cakes, ... made from vegetables, very fresh.\r\n\r\nPrice range: 30,000 - 60,000 VND / person', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS-3-NjBIDiFIj0X_bM5zIh4RzF1mhifqwktg&usqp=CAU@\r\nhttps://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRWklsQJSQ3XLhgwYChErhVRUlipxTOfDwSlA&usqp=CAU@\r\nhttps://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcR5GSDpM2o2Oraz8Iu_Yc9EKzefZMMNG4Hmug&usqp=CAU@\r\nhttps://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTOQwQDzm7TQOCFRq_pVw6wWgCziWJJp-4TDQ&usqp=CAU', 7, '16.066094', '108.219808'),
(18, 'Vegetarian rice in Âu Lạc', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSjRe_UzJRtncZoUhVG2O_vJMUgkAwOqXZwZQ&usqp=CAU', 'Vegetarian Au Au Lac - 60 Nguyen Du, Van Thach Thang, Hai Chau District', 'Au Lac vegetarian rice has a very clean and airy space which is a favorite destination for many food lovers because the menu is plentiful. The dishes in the restaurant are made according to the method of traditional vegetarian dishes from rice, noodles to fried vegetarian seafood, ... with \"beautiful\" colors and rich flavors.\r\n\r\nPrice range: 30,000 - 50,000 VND / person', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRU6J2o2WhESTw57tQBlPEJgEfCgVBaLYPSxg&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRHbfdYMYlUG_NDfLYsORC--QqW4O6Ax4xmtw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTEEjVdotMf-q-KyvfH65sl-BHY7yVbzO3ljg&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS_-R_8G3dqvzaBvbXR71nDy7aQYsDLiRR68A&usqp=CAU', 9, '16.075094', '108.221123'),
(19, 'Banh Canh Duong Ray ', 'https://images.foody.vn/res/g3/21918/prof/s576x330/foody-mobile-foody-banh-canh-duon-223-635852692120211323.jpg', 'Ganh canh is located at K77A / 09 Le Do, Chinh Gian, Thanh Khe, Da Nang, conveniently located to serve dishes, Vietnamese (salty), Vietnamese (vegetarian), European , Asian, Budget, Fast Food, Beverag', 'Ganh canh is located at K77A / 09 Le Do, Chinh Gian, Thanh Khe, Da Nang, conveniently located to serve dishes, Vietnamese (salty), Vietnamese (vegetarian), European , Asian, Budget, Fast Food, Beverages, Fruit, Fresh, reasonable prices according to customer needs from On Demand will make you delicious.', 'https://images.foody.vn/res/g3/21918/prof/s576x330/foody-mobile-foody-banh-canh-duon-223-635852692120211323.jpg@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQhuCk6Z3MlbXO6RhLHcsO1bfezFpThx5oYtQ&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQc7_fTF9KKzwDQPSR0j9QNGRpUMTlqB8neOw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTQg20ols3z0KD0OsgTrE0hqvQ34foIlO60iA&usqp=CAU', 8, '16.069027', '108.201947'),
(20, 'My Casa Restaurant', 'https://danangfantasticity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/mycasa2.jpg', 'Address: 52 Vo Nghia, Son Tra District, Da Nang', 'In Da Nang, you are familiar with traditional dishes and you want to innovate to more exotic dishes, try changing to European instead of Asian dishes to see how the palate. Check out the list of European restaurants below!\r\nIs a Spanish restaurant with a modern cuisine style. The restaurant is run by the Spaniards, fresh food is delivered directly from far away Spain and is processed by chefs into delicious European dishes. Coming here, you will receive a diverse food menu with delicious dishes from the head chef with over 15 years of cooking experience in famous restaurants in the world. Come to Merkat restaurant and enjoy Spanish cuisine.', 'https://danangfantasticity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/mycasa2.jpg@https://danangfantasticity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/mycasa1.jpg@https://danangfantasticity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/mycasa6.jpg@https://danangfantasticity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/mycasa4.jpg@https://danangfantasticity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/mycasa5.jpg', 10, '16.071752', '108.242755'),
(21, 'Pool House Restaurant', 'https://www.intercontinentalsanctuarycove.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel/public/POOL%20HOUSE_THE%20CAROUSEL%20SIZE.jpg?itok=qyLqhR2m&timestamp=1569816222', 'Hyatt Regency Danang Resort & Spa Truong Sa Street, Hoa Hai Ward, Ngu Hanh Son District, Da Nang 59499 Vietnam', 'Overlooking the Resort’s stunning one acre beach lagoon and nearby to the Terrace Pool and Spa, The Pool House provides the perfect spot to quench your thirst or tide your hunger till dinner. Offering an array of local craft beers, sangria pitchers, mocktails, an extensive cocktail selection and casual cuisine, the poolside menu ensures you won’t need to leave your daybed for too long.\r\n\r\nAppealing to those seeking relaxation and revitalisation, the nearby Adult’s Zone is the perfect sanctuary to unwind while the adjacent Family Fun Zone promises to create magical moments the whole family will remember for years to come. \r\n\r\nIn the know tip: Order a Coconut Cocktail - either CocoTiny or Bon Entendeur - for the perfect poolside Instagram moment.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/0a/fc/a3/4c/pool-house-restaurant.jpg@https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/07/31/bf/1b/pool-house-restaurant.jpg@https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/11/32/be/4b/a-gf-chicken-dish-sorry.jpg@https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-l/11/32/be/4b/a-gf-chicken-dish-sorry.jpg', 11, '16.077131', '108.243712'),
(22, 'Lucky Bee homestay', 'https://www.luxstay.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Lucky-Bee-homestay-da-nang.jpg', 'Lucky Bee is quite convenient location 453 Kinh Duong Vuong, Hoa Minh, Lien Chieu, Da Nang near the ideal tourist attraction to attract tourists from all directions.', 'Lucky Bee is quite convenient location 453 Kinh Duong Vuong, Hoa Minh, Lien Chieu, Da Nang near the ideal tourist attraction attracting tourists from all directions. Homestay is located right on Lien Chieu street near the beach, the international airport is easy to move for checking in or entry. With such convenient location, spoiled for watching the beach, sunset to play with relatives. Lucky Bee is near the locations of Han River Bridge, Love Lock Bridge and near many other attractive places. However, Lucky Bee has a limitation that is a bit far from the city center, homestay will be suitable for those who want to find quiet, peaceful accommodation, away from urban noise.Review room quality at Lucky Bee\r\nLucky Bee homestay Da Nang builds traditional guest houses, simple and clean design. The room is built in the middle combined with the cafe on the first and third floors, the view is quite impressive with the majestic, dreamy, cool mountain landscape. Especially, here is extremely quiet, suitable for relaxing.\r\n\r\nA simple traditional model will be the favorite address for foreign tourists who want to explore Vietnamese cultural traditions. It will be more interesting to learn how to cook wine from the indigenous people, to learn how to cook special dishes in the traditional way of Danang people.Not only bring quiet space, cool mountain view, Lucky Bee homestay Da Nang also has a bar serving refreshment services, gathering fun of tourists. Sitting on the 3rd floor view, you can enjoy the natural landscapes of Da Nang mountains and forests with the freshest soul.\r\n\r\nThe Lucky Bee homestay family also prepares you for a lot of intellectual and entertaining games such as billiard tables and table tennis.Lucky\'s room is built quite friendly, close as your home so. The room is designed according to a simple decor, taking the white color as the main theme, making the house become more luxurious, sophisticated and eye-catching.The host here is quite friendly, likable, contact many lovely lovely owners always guide themselves wholeheartedly \"go here to eat delicious, play here cheap\". I was quite impressed with her gentle manners, full of hospitable Da Nang people.\r\n\r\nIt was really fun to come to Lucky Bee homestay Da Nang, if I have the opportunity to come to this city, I will definitely come here.\r\n\r\nYou see the benefit of going is that instead of sitting at home imagining everything, you can now go to the new lands to test it and explore it. So why hesitate any longer, without visiting Luxstay and book your backpack to go to explore the beautiful coastal city yet.', 'https://www.luxstay.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Lucky-Bee-homestay-da-nang-2-768x576.jpg@https://www.luxstay.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Lucky-Bee-homestay-da-nang-1_1-768x513.jpg@https://www.luxstay.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Lucky-Bee-homestay-da-nang-1_2-768x513.jpg@https://www.luxstay.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Lucky-Bee-homestay-da-nang.jpg', 13, '16.080719', '108.160346'),
(23, 'French village', 'https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/lang-phap-it_hoangan.jpg', 'The French village is located in the area of ​​Ba Na Hill entertainment area - a destination that attracts both domestic and foreign tourists in Da Nang over time.', 'Arriving in the French village on the top of Ba Na Hill, you seem to be lost in a completely different fairy paradise amidst the fanciful smog of ancient castles. This place is also an ideal destination for those who want to find a place to relax, relax after hard working days or those who are passionate about discovering ancient European architecture.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nWhat is ‘hot’ French village in Ba Na Hill?\r\nThe French village is designed with 7 main areas, each of which is a piece of music with different levels and colors. When you come here, you can admire an elegant France, proud with the ancient architectural complex of St Denis Church, Chateau De Chenonceau castle, ... or a peaceful and romantic France with the old village. beautiful as the fairy with the unique shape of the seashell Conques Aveyron and the famous towns of Denis, Eze.If you\'ve had fun in the French village of Da Nang, you definitely have to visit the following highlights: the old French town of Britany with thick stone walls with sharp sloping roofs and vast, spacious courtyards. St Denis Street with a quiet, peaceful space, Chateau De Chenonceau castle with astonishing beauty and elegance, ancient and finally the small Apremont sur Allier village with peaceful space and scenery untouched.In addition, you can also stop by the Postal Café to enjoy a cup of hot coffee in the cold air of Ba Na Hill and drop your soul to the melodious French melodies, soaring through the music of the people street doctor.', 'https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/lang-phap-it_hoangan.jpg@https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/lang-phap-mikestukami.jpg@https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/momm-mom.mom3008.jpg@https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/lang-phap_kim-nin-hau.jpg@https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/thi-tran-britany.jpg@https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/lang-chaue-justcallme.jpg@https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/lang-agilin-sen7998.jpg@https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/thanh-duong-august-dung-88.jpg@https://luhanhvietnam.com.vn/du-lich/vnt_upload/news/05_2020/Ngoi_Lang_Conques_Aveyron-ruxian-ruan.jpg', 15, '15.996618', '107.988535'),
(24, 'Cultural and Cinema Center Da Nang City', 'https://danangsensetravel.com/view/at_da-nang-xay-dung-trung-tam-van-hoa-the-thao-cong-nhan_642889f651c9dc908f570943a751e901.jpg', 'The Culture and Sports Center has an area of ​​4,500 m2, including a 250-seat hall, a working room, 2 volleyball courts, 2 mini football fields, a garage, a technical infrastructure system ... constru', 'TP Da Nang currently has more than 70,000 workers living and working in 6 industrial parks in Lien Chieu, Son Tra, Cam Le and Hoa Vang districts. Particularly, Hoa Khanh Industrial Zone has nearly 30,000 workers. With the desire to take care of and protect workers\' legitimate and legitimate rights and interests; the putting into use of the Cultural and Sports Center to serve the needs of cultural and sports activities, physical training of workers.\r\n \r\nThe Culture and Sports Center has an area of ​​4,500 m2, including a 250-seat hall, a working room, 2 volleyball courts, 2 mini football fields, a garage, a technical infrastructure system ... construction over 3 months, with a total investment of over 4.2 billion.The Center also has a legal consultancy office of the Trade Union of industrial parks, which is the place to receive, consult, receive and process information, support the construction of labor relations in the area of ​​the industrial park. Karma.\r\n \r\nMs. Dang Thi Kim Lien, President of HCMC Labor Federation. Da Nang, on behalf of the Standing Committee of the City Labor Federation, hopes that the City Party Committee and People\'s Committee of Da Nang will continue to pay attention and create favorable conditions on land fund and funding for the model to be replicated in other industrial parks in the city. .', 'https://danangsensetravel.com/view/at_da-nang-xay-dung-trung-tam-van-hoa-the-thao-cong-nhan_642889f651c9dc908f570943a751e901.jpg@https://danangsensetravel.com/view/at_da-nang-xay-dung-trung-tam-van-hoa-the-thao-cong-nhan_f147af2b37466ef45e7fd83b8d57e7cd.jpg', 18, '16.054872', '108.234419'),
(25, 'Dai Nam relics in Da Nang', 'https://dulichfun.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Kinh-nghiem-du-lich-Dai-Nam-Van-Hien-01.png', 'Location: Nai Nam communal house is now in Nam Son block, Hoa Cuong ward, Hai Chau district, Da Nang city.', 'Dai Nam Communal House is the most typical historical-cultural site of Da Nang city. Let\'s travel to Vietnam to learn about this historical Da Nang historical site.\r\nLocation: Nai Nam communal house is now in Nam Son block, Hoa Cuong ward, Hai Chau district, Da Nang city.\r\nCharacteristics: Historical vestige of Nai Nam communal house, in addition to the value of an architectural and artistic relic, is also one of the typical intact typical communal communal houses in Da Nang city.\r\n\r\nDai Nam communal house in Da Nang was built in the year of the year of the horse (1905) from the contribution of the local people, worshiping the tutelary god of integrity, the duty of earth spirits and the ancestors of the village.Dai Nam communal house imprints with historical and cultural imprints of the Nguyen Dynasty. Traveling to Danang to visit this famous monument, visitors will have the opportunity to admire the special architecture of this famous ancient temple. Yin-yang roof tiles, brick walls, on the roof of the house is a dragon flanking the moon, proclaiming the peace, biting bats, expressed through the art of grafting porcelain, elaborately and beautifully. Inside, there are 3 compartments, 2 wings, the main section is 11.7m long, 7.9m wide, the post-deep 3.9m wide, 4.1m long. There are 4 rows of 20 columns with jackfruit wood, height from 2.5m - 4.5m. The structure of the rafters follows the \"husband and wife - fake hand\". The gable part is skillfully and intricately carved through the talented hands of the craftsman Kim Bong (Hoi An), showing topics such as: long carp carp, grapes of the grapes, and floral and floral motifs, flowers.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTJvYIVySxjgxGbjP3Go9YuwKafzV16YnKxhQ&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTB7_batZ8GhvTHoqYEUXAKtlE9kPQN_Nl8Aw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSolWzDoBCJphAX-xqjjdLWZp787wZazD9o8g&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS_G-CaNsspwTj5wqMYa6d4-mYxkCyY7yG0uw&usqp=CAU', 19, '16.036971', '108.227467'),
(26, 'Danang Souvenirs & Cafe', 'https://kinhnghiemdulichdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-1.jpg', 'Address: No. 34 Bạch Đằng, Hải Châu - Đà Nẵng', '1. Danang Souvenirs & Cafe - Souvenir Selling Place In Danang\r\nTet holiday throttle, hunt hard sale with shopee - Discount up to 50% on Da Nang dry specialties here\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAddress: No. 34 Bạch Đằng, Hải Châu - Đà Nẵng\r\nTelephone: +84 (0236) 3827 999\r\nLocated right in the city center, close to the 5-star Novotel hotel and in front of the Danang Administrative Center. Danang Souvenirs & Café is a suitable destination for many domestic and foreign tourists. Especially here is a stop for office workers to enjoy coffee and visit souvenirs.It is not just for a drink or chatting with friends. But also can find creative inspiration at work. By seeing a lot of souvenirs designed exclusively by Danang Souvenirs company.With 2 main product lines: tourism souvenir products and business-service gift products. Types of products can be mentioned such as: Bags, hats, glasses, notebooks, T-shirts, beer bottles, post cards, stuffed buns ... Interesting, funny pictures of Da Nang are recorded on each product.', 'https://kinhnghiemdulichdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-1.jpg@https://kinhnghiemdulichdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-1.jpg@https://kinhnghiemdulichdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-1.jpg@https://kinhnghiemdulichdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/6.jpg@', 21, '16.077935', '108.223699'),
(27, 'Dung Tuyet fine art stone carving establishment', 'https://danangz.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/dung-tuyet-768x414.jpg', 'Dung Tuyet stone carving establishment is located in Non Nuoc stone village, Da Nang city', '8 locations selling cheap handicrafts in Da Nang\r\nDung Tuyet fine art stone carving establishment\r\nDung Tuyet stone carving establishment is located in Non Nuoc stone village, Da Nang city. Located under the famous Marble Mountains, this place is famous at home and abroad for a long tradition of stone carving, with many talented artisans and thousands of people involved in manufacturing.All products are sculpted by hand, each finished product requires a lot of time, through many stages, from a rock and then sketching, choosing colors and sizes, to roughing, producing shape, cool, then polish.\r\n\r\nSpecialized facilities:\r\nSculpting all kinds of portraits, art, ... monolithic marble. \\ Wholesale and retail of fine art stone items.\r\nProducing fine art stone goods on request.\r\nTransportation and installation on demand.\r\nContact information about Dung Tuyet fine art stone base\r\nAddress: Lot 16-17 Trường Sa, Ngu Hanh Son District\r\nEmail: dungtuyetstone@gmail.com\r\nWebsite: www.dungtuyetstone.com\r\nHotline: 0913 430 171 - 0935556064', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQox5vARUbungeJcp7nqTEw48uTqZM-jcTtKQ&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcROPC94OOgnS5f3vvRi1X0Pk7_9sLTAXzAiDA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTzi-lPr0sUKm--2znjMGyl3Y5RY2-5B-5eoQ&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcR1m_wCeID8h0JpbAAbbCpVqpuvVCJ7MFkk0A&usqp=CAU', 22, '16.002570', '108.266927'),
(28, 'BQ', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRuAQdekKaQnaR3qtKrTmjZL3x4aYs9oeGE8w&usqp=CAU', 'Địa chỉ:\r\n\r\n246 Ông Ích Khiêm, Đà Nẵng\r\n57 Lê Duẩn, Đà Nẵng\r\n49 Nguyễn Văn Thoại, Đà Nẵng\r\n147 Ông Ích Đường, Đà Nẵng\r\n09 Âu Cơ, Đà Nẵng', 'BQ\r\nThe BQ brand is an acronym for “BEST QUALITY” with the working orientation of “good quality” for all aspects of operation. BQ shoe brand is no stranger to customers.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBQ is famous for its branches and shops present in all provinces and cities with good quality shoes, guaranteed, diverse designs ... With customer support services, free delivery, after payment upon receipt, 30 days flexible exchange; Since then, BQ has received the love and trust from customers over the years. BQ always gives customers the discount programs such as golden hour shock prices, extremely hot promotions.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIn addition to the women\'s shoes, in the BQ store system, there are also elegant elegant and dynamic men\'s shoes. BQ is proud to be a Vietnamese brand trusted by Vietnamese. Coming to BQ is coming with professionalism and fashion.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFOR DETAILS PLEASE CONTACT:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAddress:\r\n\r\n246 Ong Ich Khiem, Da Nang\r\n57 Le Duan, Da Nang\r\n49 Nguyen Van Thoai, Da Nang\r\n147 Ong Ich Duong, Da Nang\r\n09 Au Co, Da Nang\r\nHotline: 0236.6252.252\r\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/giaybq/\r\nWebsite: https://www.giaybq.com.vn/', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRuAQdekKaQnaR3qtKrTmjZL3x4aYs9oeGE8w&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQWensmnwz17nPG0GQsBs-UUKLXOD6SQo7g2w&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSpAY7sFD7JWmio23ok4__2YexqoCiqcH0vKg&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQg59g4jRjv-O_tDPs7q8JVfJpimnbkuYHzJw&usqp=CAU', 23, '16.067779', '108.214143'),
(29, 'Veston Tran', 'https://danangz.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/11-15.jpg', 'Address: 146 Nguyen Hoang, Da Nang', 'You are in Da Nang and you are wondering where to sew vest is both good, beautiful, and reasonably priced, Veston Tran is one of the perfect choices for you. This is a place specializing in tailoring or renting men\'s suits (young vest), wedding vest, dust vest in Danang.With many years of experience in tailoring, Veston Tran has gradually asserted his position in the Veston fashion market as well as the office fashion.\r\n\r\nTran vest is also known as one of the fastest updated vest trends of the year, Especially when you come here, you will be carefully advised by the staff about the vest design to suit the body shape and trend. .\r\n\r\nContact information:\r\n\r\nAddress: 146 Nguyen Hoang, Da Nang\r\nPhone: 0888888416', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTq8yl7FwIrhMQ6IZMBtXvX2wZSu6G6yUmTwQ&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQR3g7DohKDY4LqA_cfy5azzVZXsqOK-THKsw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcR1AnXgwh62WaLipo-ziEipBa_TuSaFmyjnNg&usqp=CAU', 24, '16.062078', '108.213855'),
