(41, 'Russian Consulate in Da Nang', 'https://dulichlive.com/da-nang/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/08/Lanh-su-quan-o-Da-Nang-lanh-su-Nga.webp', 'Address: 5th Floor, Green Plaza Building, 223 Tran Phu Street, Phuoc Ninh Ward, Hai Chau District, Da Nang', 'Russian Consulate in Da Nang\r\nAddress: 5th Floor, Green Plaza Building, 223 Tran Phu Street, Phuoc Ninh Ward, Hai Chau District, Da Nang\r\nPhone: (0236) 382 23 80 or (0236) 381 85 28\r\nWorking hours: Receive visa applications on Mondays, Tuesdays, and Thursdays from 10am - 12pm on weekdays, return documents on Monday to Friday from 10am - 12pm every week. No public holidays and public holidays\r\nWebsite: rusconsdanang.mid.ruThe Russian Consulate in Da Nang is the address to apply for a visa for Vietnamese citizens who want to come to Russia to work, study or travel or travel. When you want to apply for a visa to go to Russia, you do not need to go to Hanoi or Ho Chi Minh City like other country consulates. This is one of the foreign consulates in Da Nang that you can apply for a visa directly.\r\n\r\nRegarding the fee of the Russian consulate in Da Nang for visa / visa issuance as follows:\r\n\r\n- Single entry visa\r\n\r\n4 - 20 working days: 720k\r\n1 - 3 working days: 1tr440k\r\n - Visa on entry 2 times\r\n\r\n4 - 20 working days: 1tr152k\r\n1 - 3 working days: 2tr304k\r\n - Entry visa many times\r\n\r\n4 - 20 working days: 2tr160k\r\n1 - 3 working days: 4tr320k', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRwoVIu8ho0td6pTN-NSr5MIuC94P7okpB20A&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSLprwWpn8RdDKcQ-m2c4ZABKJVSrEGzfOWTA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRBXGlW0W84rF0hCgO5_75yqjR9ltLpqjNPxw&usqp=CAU', 36, '16.078004', '108.222959'),
