(43, 'Skincare Thien Nhan Beauty Salon', 'https://toplist.vn/images/800px/skincare-vien-tham-my-thien-nhan-483173.jpg', 'Skincare Thien Nhan Beauty Salon. Located at 02 Tien Son 7, Hai Chau District, this will be an ideal place for not only sisters in the province but also a beauty and relaxation spot for tourists comin', 'Skincare Thien Nhan Beauty Salon\r\nAt the top of this list, there is no more worthy name than Skincare Thien Nhan Beauty Salon. Located at 02 Tien Son 7, Hai Chau District, this will be an ideal place for not only sisters in the province but also a beauty spot and a relaxing place for visitors to Danang.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nUnderstanding the psychology of women, Dr. Tran Thien Nhan has invested in Skincare room with airy modern equipment to help women feel comfortable refurbishing their beauty. In addition, the team of technicians always work enthusiastically, dedicatedly and professionally trained to help customers have memorable experiences.Outstanding services\r\n\r\nSkin rejuvenation using Hifu technology, PRP, salmon DNA\r\nIntensive skin care and restoration\r\nAcne Treatment\r\nMelasma, freckles, age spots\r\nTreating keloid scars, concave scars, pitted scars\r\nSpray tattoos, sculpt, remove tattoos\r\nHair removal, high-tech slimming\r\n5 reasons to experience Skincare Thien Nhan Beauty Salon\r\n\r\nDermatologists directly examine, consult and carry out treatment and skin rejuvenation procedures\r\nElegant, cozy, close by the presence of plants, flowers\r\nDiverse services, using products derived from natural herbs\r\nHighly skilled technicians help you completely relax and receive the best treatment\r\nTaking the lead in investing in modern equipment and machinery to apply to the beauty processes, creating high efficiency and long-term.\r\nLuxury cosmetic applications are imported genuine, creating a sense of security for customers when beauty.\r\nMSc.BS. Thanh Loan goes directly to customers\r\n\r\n\"A hundred hearing not equal to one seeing, one hundred seeing not equal to one try.\" Only when you come and experience it for yourself will you feel all that unique traits.FOR DETAILS PLEASE CONTACT:\r\nBeauty Salon Thien Nhan\r\nAddress: 02 Tiên Sơn 7, Hải Châu District, Đà Nẵng City (Opposite Eye Hospital)\r\nHotline / zalo: 0901 133 733\r\nFanpage: https://www.facebook.com/VienThamMyThienNhan/\r\nWebsite: http://thammythiennhan.com/\r\nOpen: 8:30 - 18:00 (all days of the week)', 'https://toplist.vn/images/800px/skincare-vien-tham-my-thien-nhan-483173.jpg@https://toplist.vn/images/800px/skincare-vien-tham-my-thien-nhan-483174.jpg@', 38, '16.036872', '108.219873');
