(44, 'Ngoc Dung Beauty Salon', 'https://danangaz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/tham-my-vien-ngoc-dung-157050-min.jpg', 'Address: 95 Nguyen Van Linh, Nam Duong, Hai Chau, Da Nang', '1. Ngoc Dung Beauty Salon- The Beauty Salon of Danang\r\nAddress: 95 Nguyen Van Linh, Nam Duong, Hai Chau, Da Nang\r\nPhone: 0236 3584 594 - 0939 060 756\r\nWebsite: https://www.thammyvienngocdung.com/\r\nNgoc Dung Beauty Salon is one of the leading cosmetic brands in Vietnam. Ngoc Dung Beauty Salon in Da Nang is proud to be one of the system of 6 branches across the country. With the purpose of meeting the diverse needs of customers as well as to affirm the brand value, Ngoc Dung Beauty Salon has always been constantly learning and applying many modern aesthetic technologies and services. In order to bring the most perfect beauty to dear customers with the highest quality and service.Aesthetic services at TMV Ngoc Dung:\r\nCosmetic Surgery\r\nBeauty services such as: Lifting eyebrows, creating double eyelids, removing lower eyelids, pressing eyelids\r\nRhinoplasty services such as: S-line rhinoplasty, nasal shrinkage, nasal cartilage wrap\r\nHigh-tech aesthetics\r\nNew IPL is used in root hair removal, acne treatment, acne treatment, melasma ...\r\nLRF Laser technology helps to make people sick and eliminate excess fat, helping the body become firmer and leaner.\r\nHifu technology helps reduce wrinkles, beautiful skin, creating V-line face\r\nCryolipolysisBesides, this is a prestigious beauty place with a team of good doctors, methodically trained on professional qualifications and skills. And many years of training in countries with strengths in the aesthetic industry such as the US and South Korea. Skin care rooms, high-tech, surgical rooms with modern machinery ensure the standards of the Ministry of Health. Diverse and modern equipment system imported directly from the United States.\r\n\r\nWith the motto \"Beautiful forever with time\", Ngoc Dung Beauty Salon will definitely be the perfect choice for you to embellish and maintain timeless beauty.', 'https://danangaz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/tham-my-vien-ngoc-dung-157050-min.jpg@https://danangaz.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1-min-8.jpg@', 39, '16.060140', '108.213238'),
(45, 'Vinmec Danang International General Hospital', 'https://vinmec-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/10_12_2018_04_29_55_993835.jpeg', 'Located at 30/4 Street, Residential Area No. 4 Nguyen Tri Phuong, Hoa Cuong Bac Ward, Hai Chau District, Da Nang City', 'Vinmec International Hospital Danang is the sixth hospital in the Vinmec Health System, officially put into operation in September 2017. Located at 30/4 Street, Residential Area No. 4 Nguyen Tri Phuong, Hoa Cuong Bac Ward, Hai Chau District, Da Nang City, the Hospital has a total construction area of ​​over 37 thousand m2, including 9 floors and 1 floor tunnel, scale of 222 beds, enough to serve thousands of patients each year.\r\nVinmec Danang Medical Registration Hospital gathered a team of leading experts and doctors, highly qualified, experienced, always devoted to the patients. The comprehensive investment in world-leading facilities and equipment contributes to the improvement of diagnosis and treatment efficiency. As a member of the most modern health system in the country, and also the first private health system in Vietnam, there are 02 hospitals that achieved JCI, Vinmec Da Nang international hospital, proud to bring medical services. international standards and become the leading healthcare address for people in the Central Region.', 'https://vinmec-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/10_12_2018_04_29_55_993835.jpeg@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQ-dsEU2tT-oYEjkycgUl7PcowtiUsst7GB-A&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQQsul1S8SIdq2ee49A37z7bZRt2YhbUfNsfg&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcR6Oj-I4r_2r-WImEd6hLrB6L74xfZ1jgV8wg&usqp=CAU', 40, '16.038906', '108.211320'),
(46, 'California Fitness & Yoga Da Nang', 'https://www.cfyc.com.vn/images_server/themes/celebration/img/club/mobile/danang/club1/2.jpg', 'Address: City Post Office Building, 2nd Floor, 271 Nguyen Van Linh, Vinh Trung Ward, Thanh Khe District, Da Nang.', 'Certainly California Fitness & Yoga is the center for \"best\" fitness and fitness training today in Da Nang City. California Fitness & Yoga Da Nang is located in the city post office building, with extremely spacious space and invested in a modern exercise machine system, meeting international standards. This Danang Gym has a team of highly qualified, experienced and dedicated coaches to help members achieve efficiency quickly. In addition, California Fitness & Yoga Da Nang also has many disciplines for customers who register to practice such as Gym, Yoga, Dance, Kickfit or group fitness ... You need to participate in training here, maybe Contact Danang Gym gym directly with the following address:\r\n\r\n- Address: City Post Office Building, 2nd Floor, 271 Nguyen Van Linh, Vinh Trung Ward, Thanh Khe District, Da Nang.\r\n\r\n- Phone: 02367109299.\r\n\r\n- Subjects: Gym, Yoga, Dance, Kickfit, group fitness.\r\n\r\n- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/cfycvn/.', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSVy4IASkY-i2XqJXYueMVrnwdU9N6jncoX9Q&usqp=CAU@https://www.cfyc.com.vn/images_server/themes/celebration/img/club/mobile/danang/club1/2.jpg@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSLtbrZaucvCJHkvps0wSo3SDt-ijsXmA_d_A&usqp=CAU@https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMBMK52178YNdDQmRkyckBP_Ozrl8tdosIJobKB=w408-h306-k-no', 41, '16.059900', '108.211746'),
(47, 'Vietnamese French dentistry', 'https://toplist.vn/images/800px/nha-khoa-viet-phap-134336.jpg', 'Facility 1: 459 Le Duan, Da Nang', 'Vietnamese French dentistry\r\nVietnamese French Dental was born with the goal of providing customers with the best service of oral health care, both professional and quality service. Coming to dentistry, you will feel the kindness and comfort as being at your own home. With the motto \"Beautiful smile ... changes your life\", we want to bring healthy, beautiful teeth to help you always be confident anytime, anywhere. Dentistry is one of the most prestigious clinics in Danang. In the future, Viet Phap Clinic will make every effort to bring the best services to our customers.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe reason you should beautify Vietnamese French dental ears?\r\n\r\nopen and clear space\r\nMany of the leading specialties in the field of maxillofacial teeth and cosmetic surgery.\r\nEquipped with new generation machines\r\nAttentive and professional service attitude\r\nConsulting team dedicated, professional serviceVietnamese-French dental services:\r\n\r\nOrthodontic coral - pinched - deviated\r\nWhitening\r\nCosmetic porcelain restorations\r\nPeriodontal treatment, orthodontics, braces\r\nReference price list:\r\n\r\nWhitening: 1,200,000 VND - 1,800,000 VND\r\nExamination and counseling: Free of charge\r\nQuicklime: 100,000 VND - 150,000 VND\r\nFillings: 100,000 VND - 150,000 VND\r\nAttaching dental stones: VND 600,000 - VND 1,200,000\r\nDental implant: VND 12,000,000 - VND 20,000,000\r\nCONTACT INFORMATION:Address:\r\n\r\nFacility 1: 459 Le Duan, Da Nang\r\nFacility 2: 113-115 Le Do\r\nPhone: 0236.6288811\r\nHotline: 0961954666\r\nWebiste: http://nhakhoavietphapdn.com\r\nEmail: nhakhoathammyvietphap@gmail.com', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRKFQ7yOr-Umr5neWID9x4DYuDDcT9QrVvdCA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS6MTuHWONaB6L4Q64uBWUg7n4WBAYMGic3cw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQXLUWkRiXH0ZRnkw02TG5JdQvtfX1x3CNOwg&usqp=CAU', 42, '16.061071', '108.210835'),
(48, 'Vinmec Danang International Hospital', 'https://dulichlive.com/da-nang/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/08/Benh-vien-o-Da-Nang-chat-luong-tot-nhat-Vinmec-Da-Nang.webp', 'Address: 30/4 Street, Residential Area No. 4 Nguyen Tri Phuong, Hoa Cuong Bac Ward, Q Hai Chau, Da Nang City', 'Vinmec Danang International Hospital\r\nAddress: 30/4 Street, Residential Area No. 4 Nguyen Tri Phuong, Hoa Cuong Bac Ward, Hai Chau District, Da Nang City\r\nPhone number: 0236 3711 111\r\nWebsite: vinmec.com\r\nAdministrative working hours: 8:00 am - 5:00 pm Monday - Friday, 8:00 am - 12:00 am Saturday afternoon, Saturday and Sunday afternoonThis is one of the hospitals in Da Nang with good doctors and top quality service today. Coming to Vinmec Da Nang hospital, everyone will be welcomed and served as a guest, everything is clean and professional, not like public hospitals. Vinmec Da Nang Hospital has many different medical examination and treatment departments to meet the medical examination and treatment needs of all patients such as pediatrics - neonatal, emergency resuscitation department, general surgery, obstetrics and gynecology, diagnosis Predicting images, testing, pharmacy, examination & internal medicine, cardiology. In general, this is a large, good quality hospital in Da Nang for families with conditions because the cost of medical examination and treatment here is very high and if there is no emergency, everyone should call for an appointment in advance. save on medical expenses.For example, the price list of some services at Vinmec Da Nang hospital is for your reference:\r\n\r\n- Emergency examination: 1.8 million\r\n\r\n- Internal medicine examination: 440k appointment in advance, not 1.1 million appointment\r\n\r\n- Specialized medical examination: with an appointment of VND 690k without an appointment of VND 1.1 million\r\n\r\n- Expert examination or out-of-office examination: VND 1.8 million\r\n\r\n- Consulting fee: consulting for under 30 minutes costs 300k, over 30 minutes costs 600k', 'https://vinmec-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/10_12_2018_04_29_55_993835.jpeg@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQeSbrklXU7U2O34_rlr_KP_rUDxJ6kRQg9lA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcR6Oj-I4r_2r-WImEd6hLrB6L74xfZ1jgV8wg&usqp=CAU', 44, '16.038916', '108.211320'),
