(51, 'Helio Center', 'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNojBrppt1sJ30a3RlXmQEi7-9MFbIdzUklt_y-=w408-h263-k-no', 'Southeast Park Memorial Park, 2/9 Street, Hoa Cuong Bac Ward, Hai Chau District, Da Nang 550000 Vietnam', 'The total area of ​​Helio Center is about 35,000 m2 making this place a popular entertainment center, not only for Danang residents but also for tourists from all over the provinces and foreign tourists. like to come here. With such a large campus, Helio Center can accommodate up to 10,000 guests in a day. On holidays, weekends, you and your family can come here to participate in extremely interesting entertainment activities, enjoy the culinary flavors from many different regions.Helio Center includes 3 main areas: Helio play, Helio kids, Food & Beverage. Each area has its own interesting style, which is consulted by experts from the US to design according to the most modern and safe standards.\r\n\r\nHelio Play is a large playroom, with an area of ​​up to 1000 m2, equipped with modern gaming machines with many different games. Especially, for Helio play games you do not need cash, all used by a Universal Card (Power Card), just swipe the card to start the fun. Multimeter card is a modern form of payment, helping players not to have cash in hand, while playing can control the information of the card such as account balance, the number of tickets available, the program Enjoy special promotions and other benefits when using the card.There are three types of Power Card used: regular, pink and yellow. The card is usually a blue card that is freely distributed to all customers who come to play. Pink card is a card that customers have provided information to register as a member of Helio Center with a bright pink color. When you use this card, you will receive a discount of 20% for all services except for food service. The yellow card is for customers who are close to Helio Center with a bright pink color. There are also many other incentives for yellow cards such as: 5% off when booking a party at Helio Center, receive birthday gifts, receive preferential information from many other programs. If you come here to play, you should make a Power Card for ease of playing, the way is very simple, you just need to go to the front desk to get the free card, if you register as a member, you should spend less time providing information. personal.', 'https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNojBrppt1sJ30a3RlXmQEi7-9MFbIdzUklt_y-=w408-h263-k-no@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSCdrhR8kYE0xXxCYBo3_kpUIRuM-C0hdIPug&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRya1gxhhtf5wBVyLSWYCvhwVl23OVAih25fQ&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS5xLZ2NdLt6lr5EmRupeCDx_SeS8_F8A6onQ&usqp=CAU', 48, '16.037479', '108.224572'),
(52, 'Danang Exhibition Fair Center', 'http://ndn.com.vn/uploads/images/tthoichotrienlam_dn(1).jpg', 'Location: Cach Mang Thang 8 Street, Cam Le District, Da Nang City', 'Danang Exhibition Fair Project is located on Cach Mang Thang 8 Street, Khue Trung Ward, Cam Le District, Da Nang City\r\nProject brief:\r\nInvestor: Danang Department of Commerce and Tourism\r\nConstruction unit: Danang Housing Development and Investment Joint Stock Company\r\nLocation: Cach Mang Thang 8 Street, Cam Le District, Da Nang City\r\n\r\nScale works:\r\nShowroom (3 floors) and outside technical infrastructure.\r\nContract\'s value: 20,546,103,000 VND\r\nDuration: 2006-2008', 'http://ndn.com.vn/uploads/images/tthoichotrienlam_dn(1).jpg@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT037mGeFFcVMdFX_f_XEpMigZv--iLO-dIuA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTlaUdAhS1ARdFlyGIlbdyTpVTtfZ0P1Di4zw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSvAihKQfJ535CoVWyJobI3yVWILqNZBdF8Zw&usqp=CAU', 49, '16.022097', '108.217339'),
(53, 'Starlight Danang', 'https://dacsandanangtran.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Starlight-da-nang.jpg', 'Starlight Danang Cinema is located at TT Nguyen Kim - Dien Bien Phu, Da Nang, built with Hollywood cinema standards', 'Starlight Danang\r\n4th Floor - Nguyen Kim Building, 46 Dien Bien Phu, Thanh Khe District, Tp. Danang\r\n\r\n Starlight Danang Ticket Map\r\nStarlight Danang Cinema is located at Nguyen Kim - Dien Bien Phu, Da Nang, built with Hollywood cinema standard, Dolby 7.1 sound standard, large and sharp screen. Starlight Danang is one of the bustling movie theaters in the most livable city in Vietnam today. As part of the Starlight entertainment chain, audiences here will have many entertainment options before and after the show. With an integrated milk tea system, Starlight Da Nang is truly the number 1 entertainment destination for young audiences.', 'https://dacsandanangtran.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Starlight-da-nang.jpg@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQOodEDZNunV4eQui91-1WDcjrD6Ml-KuPTGA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcR8n-3RbzSFhmvv5nAJgE61meVMBsDF1ATbIw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT_Z1BwLlpez8emcJldpcFYjSXuniByHKv0mQ&usqp=CAU', 50, '16.066306', '108.203343'),
(54, '29-3 Danang Park', 'https://danangz.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Congvien293DaNang-768x508.jpg', 'Ho Park March 29, Thac Gian, Thanh Khe, Da Nang 550000, Vietnam', '1. Danang 29-3 Park - a green area in the middle of the street\r\nFirst of all, we have to mention the 29-3 park, the first one in Danang. Considered the green lung of the city with cool and fresh air, the 29/3 park has an area of ​​over 20 hectares divided into many entertainment and entertainment areas.In the park of 29/3 park, every corner is shady covered with old trees. In the middle of the park, there is a large lake making the park space more fresh. Thanks to the fresh air, always cool, this place always attracts people to play, fishing, exercise, collective activities.In the play area for children, families have fun in the spacious playground with many games such as ferris wheel, electric car, slide, laughing house…. In the green, shady areas are groups of young people gathered together to sing and practice music. Or the area around the lake is always crowded with anglers. From young people who still go to school to elderly doctors - they come to enjoy the fresh, cool air here, avoiding the hustle and bustle of the city.\r\n\r\nMarch 29 Park in Da Nang is the amusement spot of the city people every spring. Every New Year comes, the park is bustling with flower markets, flower streets, food and shops displaying red couplets, calligraphy, folk paintings,', 'https://danangz.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Congvien293DaNang-768x508.jpg@https://danangz.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/cong-vien-29-3-3.jpg@https://danangz.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/da-nang-hang-ngan-nguoi-nao-nuc-ve-hoi-hoa-xuan-choi-tet-768x548.jpg', 51, '16.062963', '108.205505'),
(55, 'Hoa Xuan Stadium', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSyp6YsLXbiPjXk0iEC1rE_8XZYNShY6R5czQ&usqp=CAU', 'X6XF + P9 Hoa Xuan, Cam Le, Da Nang, Vietnam', 'Hoa Xuan Stadium is a football stadium in Cam Le District, Da Nang City, Vietnam, can accommodate up to 20,000 seats. As the home ground of SHB Da Nang, the yard has no piste and is the second yard in Vietnam after the Pleiku yard in Gia Lai used only to organize soccer matches.In the afternoon of December 14, 2016, the Management Board of Investment Projects for construction of civil and industrial works (hereinafter referred to as Project Management Unit) officially handed over the construction of Hoa Xuan Stadium to Department of Literature. chemical - Sports (VH-TT) city to promptly put into use when the 2017 V-League season is about to start. According to the V-League 2017 schedule, the match of SHB Da Nang Football Club against the Hoang Anh Gia Lai Football Club on the opening day of the tournament (January 7, 2017) is the opening match of Hoa Xuan and billion The number of matches is 1-0 in favor of the home team.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe package of construction of 4 stands A, B, C, D, football field and surrounding technical system was constructed by Danang Infrastructure Development and Construction Joint Stock Company (DCID), with a value of more than VND 300 billion. ; the package of electric lighting system for the football field was constructed by Thanh Lam Sports Co., Ltd., with a value of nearly VND 13 billion. Starting from February 21, 2013, on August 30, 2016, the project was officially completed; After that, the Department of Construction checked and agreed to organize acceptance, put it into operation and use. [1]', 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSyp6YsLXbiPjXk0iEC1rE_8XZYNShY6R5czQ&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQHa-hzE7fk09WIn_alvExMsmtxsHnr4eTYtA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTN6hncS0MzD2rN62l_eoQXxhEktDUisDxlxA&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQ4Vx5sbhVRFLChhmNsp9uGpxvUWASqmNwQDw&usqp=CAU@https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQuB46VS6yCiJvB1newYOlz_zX5H5TkBxqGuQ&usqp=CAU', 52, '15.999267', '108.223402'),
(56, 'Quán karaoke Lá Cọ', 'https://dulichlive.com/da-nang/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/06/quan-karaoke-da-nang-3.webp', 'Address: Hòa Minh 2, Liên Chiểu District, Đà Nẵng', 'La Palm karaoke bar - beautifully designed karaoke bars in Da Nang\r\nAddress: Hòa Minh 2, Liên Chiểu District, Đà Nẵng\r\nPhone: (0511) 2 440 783\r\nPrice: 50,000 VND - 165,000 VND\r\nThe beautiful, cheap karaoke bars in Da Nang cannot be ignored Palm Leaf karaoke at Hoa Minh 2 Street, Lien Chieu District. The shop is designed with luxurious and modern space with a spacious and elegant space, the cool main tones are gentle combination between white and cool blue.Along with that is the sound system, quality lighting and enthusiastic staff, reasonable price is a big plus point of La Palm karaoke bar. Especially, La Palm karaoke bar does not have the situation of increasing prices during the Tet holiday or squeezing prices with visitors from other places. Because of that, that La Palm karaoke bar has always become a favorite destination for many visitors today.', 'https://dulichlive.com/da-nang/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/06/quan-karaoke-da-nang-3.webp@https://dulichlive.com/da-nang/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/06/quan-karaoke-da-nang-3.webp@https://dulichlive.com/da-nang/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/06/quan-karaoke-da-nang-4.webp@https://dulichlive.com/da-nang/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/06/quan-karaoke-da-nang-5.webp', 53, '16.053631', '108.221516'),
(57, 'Sở Thú Vinpearl River Safari', 'https://resortdanang.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/hinh-anh-vinpearl-land.jpg', 'Binh Minh, Thang Binh, Quang Nam, Vietnam', 'Vinpearl River Safari - an animal park by boat. This is the first and only aquatic animal park in Vietnam. The special thing when visiting this wildlife zoo is that instead of you visiting by specialized vehicles. Then you will experience a new feeling when sitting on a boat. And discover the life of wildlife.\r\n\r\nComing to Vinpearl River Safari you seem to be lost in the land of the fairy world. On the mysterious and poetic Amazon river. Vietnam currently owns the largest wildlife reserve in the world. At Vinpearl Land Nam Hoi An recreational paradise. This zoo is a mecca for 39 rare and wild animals. With 42,000 individuals: Bengal tigers, white lions, rhinos, antelopes, giraffes ...Get lost in a fairytale world with Vinpearl River Safari\r\nThe wildlife here is inhabited in an appropriate ecosystem. Cared for wholeheartedly with experienced animal experts. River Safari currently supports 39 wildlife species. Such as Bengal tigers, antelopes, kangaroos, rhinos, giraffes, zebras, etc.', 'https://resortdanang.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/hinh-anh-vinpearl-land.jpg@https://resortdanang.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/du-thuyen-vinpearl-land.jpg@https://resortdanang.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/voi-vinpearl-land.jpg@https://resortdanang.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/huou-ca-co-vinpearl-land.jpg@https://resortdanang.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/hong-hac-vinpearl-land.jpg@https://resortdanang.info/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/ngua-van-vinpearl-land.jpg', 54, '15.790112', '108.412120'),
(58, 'Asia Park', 'https://www.taidanang.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/he-lo-9-khu-vui-choi-hap-dan-nhat-da-thanh-3.jpg', 'Address: No. 1 Phan Đăng Lưu street, Hoà Cường Bắc ward, Hải Châu district, Đà Nẵng', 'Asia Park\r\nAddress: No. 1 Phan Đăng Lưu street, Hoà Cường Bắc ward, Hải Châu district, Đà Nẵng\r\n\r\nSpread over an area of ​​868,694 m2, Asia Park Aisia Park located on the west bank of the Han River is a perfect combination of entertainment models in the world and unique Asian cultural features for the first time. in Viet Nam. This amusement park is divided into 3 main sections, including: outdoor amusement park with a series of unique games, cultural parks with art works, symbolic miniature architecture of 10 countries. Asian and Sun Whell areas with a cross between modernity and tradition.Coming to Asia Park, you will feel like you are stepping into a lively entertainment paradise with a series of exciting games and many fascinating experiences. For example, if you are an adventurous believer, here you will be free to scream with attractive speed games such as roller coaster, overhead tram, free fall tower, ...', 'https://www.taidanang.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/he-lo-9-khu-vui-choi-hap-dan-nhat-da-thanh-1.jpeg@https://www.taidanang.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/he-lo-9-khu-vui-choi-hap-dan-nhat-da-thanh-2.jpg@https://www.taidanang.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/he-lo-9-khu-vui-choi-hap-dan-nhat-da-thanh-5.jpg@https://www.taidanang.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/he-lo-9-khu-vui-choi-hap-dan-nhat-da-thanh-6-1.jpg@https://www.taidanang.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/he-lo-9-khu-vui-choi-hap-dan-nhat-da-thanh-3.jpg', 55, '16.038258', '108.228146');

